      "title": "Police removed \u201cGota Go Home\u201d protesters from Galle Fort",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A group of protesters who were holding banners and placards with \u2018Go Home Gota\u2019 slogans have been removed from the Galle Fort by the Police today.",
        "They ere protesting from the Galle Fort as the first Test match between Sri Lanka and Australia commenced today at the Galle cricket stadium."
